  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in the clay tajine over medium heat. Add the onion and cook until translucent. Add the garlic and ginger and cook for 1 minute. Add the cumin and coriander and cook for 1 minute. Add the bhuna sauce and cook until heated through. Add the baby pak koi and rose petals. Cook until the pak koi is cooked through. Season with salt and black pepper to taste."
